<P>
 The parade of NFL scouts that streams through UCLA practices every season had 
a new entry Tuesday. Rick Mueller has jobs with the Jacksonville Jaguars to 
offer. 
</P>
<P>
 The expansion team, which will participate in the draft for the first time in 
1995, has 14 choices in the seven rounds, including the second overall, behind 
its expansion-mate, the Carolina Panthers. 
</P>
<P>
