<P>
 Can you spare a ride? 
</P>
<P>
 The La Palma Recreation & Community Services Department is seeking drivers 
with open vehicles, such as convertibles and Jeeps, to give rides to city 
officials, celebrities and honored guests during the La Palma Days Parade on 
Nov. 12. 
</P>
<P>
 Each volunteer driver will receive a free breakfast and a 10th anniversary 
commemorative La Palma Days mug, said Ron Kenny, the city's recreation 
director. 
</P>
