A LITTLE BIT OF HISTORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Simi Valley High center Cheri Graham scored 61 points in 1981 to set a 
Southern Section single-game scoring record and help the Pioneers rout Hueneme, 
100-25. Graham made 30 of 37 shots and one of two free throws. 
