<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA102694-0089 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 092225 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 26, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 2; Sports Desk 
