</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Landmark Bancorp: The La Habra holding company for Landmark Bank earned 
$585,000, or 31 cents a share, for the third quarter.That was down from a 
profit of $702,000, or 37 cents a share, for the same period a year earlier. 
Last year's quarterly earnings, however, were boosted significantly by a 
settlement that added $540,000 to the bottom line. For the first nine months of 
