 Fewer Foreclosures: Dataquick also reported that the number of home 
foreclosures in California declined slightly during the third quarter. 
</P>
<P>
 In Orange County, foreclosures were off 8.4% to 2,535 homes. That compared to 
2,768 foreclosures for the same period a year earlier. 
