<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ethnic breakdown -- Due to inaccurate information supplied to The Times, a 
story Sunday incorrectly reported the ethnic breakdown of the staff at Cigna's 
Grand Avenue Health Care Center. The staff is 34% Latino, 29% African American, 
19% white, 17% Asian American and 1% other. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
