<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Wrong identification -- A story Saturday incorrectly identified a school 
official who urged Rio Mesa High School students to end a protest against 
Proposition 187 and return to class. The speaker was Oxnard Union High School 
District administrator Ralph Gonzalez. 
</P>
</TEXT>
